{"tid":889162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"本港專家：禽流感人傳人的機率不大","createTime":"2018-11-04T10:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T13:22:30.000Z","uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f409d13d00e2692b7bdc07ac8d71be4405e72a14","tid":889162,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:47:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n經飛沫傳播都話人傳人機會低<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野專家黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d768f6a9e8ebcd72808f2bf3e17373d1410104","tid":889162,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:47:57.000Z","msg":"日本有研究證實H7N9禽流感病毒可經空氣由飛沫傳播。<br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良表示，禽流感病毒可經飛沫傳播並非新資訊，本港於1997年已發現H5N1禽流感病毒可經禽鳥傳人，當時醫學界已有共識，這病毒可經飛沫傳人。他又說，港大於2013年已有研究證明，在雪貂之間，禽流感病毒可經飛沫傳播。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良說，雖然禽流感病毒有機會經飛沫傳播，但現階段看，在內地及東南亞出現的可傳人禽流感病毒，不論由禽鳥傳人、或由人傳人的風險屬較低；世衞對禽流感病毒包括H7N9而導致流感大流行的風險評估，仍屬於低。<br />\n<br />\n但他說，在內地確診H7N9感染人類個案中，有數十個病毒樣本屬高致病性，可於人或禽鳥造成嚴重感染，提醒市民不應掉以輕心，當前往內地時應避免到有售賣家禽的濕街市，做好個人衞生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20181104/1/9/84/何栢良-禽流感病毒有機會經飛沫傳播但人傳人風險較低-9389923.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20181104%2F1%2F9%2F84%2F%E4%BD%95%E6%A0%A2%E8%89%AF-%E7%A6%BD%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%9C%89%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E7%B6%93%E9%A3%9B%E6%B2%AB%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD%E4%BD%86%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B3%E4%BA%BA%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E8%BC%83%E4%BD%8E-9389923.html&d=lQspXP9iPwZdDHUANRnExTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2b913c81\" target=\"_blank\">https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20181104/1/9/84/何栢良-禽流感病毒有機會經飛沫傳播但人傳人風險較低-9389923.html</a>"},{"pid":"2486ff591e39ee5171f2a890d19dbf23afa03f13","tid":889162,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:48:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老味梗係信我地香港既專家啦，係咪先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40bf6e297901e7ba7944a72d9e6276e62e20650b","tid":889162,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2486ff591e39ee5171f2a890d19dbf23afa03f13","tid":889162,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:48:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老味梗係信我地香港既專家啦，係咪先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55baf54e8e88a9b35578b3b7c20fe5be45bbe875","tid":889162,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:22:30.000Z","msg":"認真POST冇人傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人真係抵鳩死<br />\n<br />\n政府同你講唔洗驚一種病 <br />\n即係呢個病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}